Class PhotoShoot

    public class PhotoShoot
extends WebCam
    This class represents the PhotoShoot panel of the window and uses the WebCam. It adds images of new/existing students to the machine learning models.
    Version:
    6
    Author:
    Arya Khokhar

      • PhotoShoot

        public PhotoShoot(java.lang.String dataDir,
                  SQLiteManager sqlManager)
        This constructor creates the files in the faces folder for machine learning and sets up the GUI components of the panel. It also contains the code for what to do when each button is pressed, including saving the images to the database.
        Parameters:
        dataDir - is the path to the directory that is passes to WebCam
        sqlManager - is the database object
